ComicInfo.Summary:
The mysterious Hurt-Bot that tried to kill Gina and Brit' with mechanisms of the Death Trap Architect is still out for blood...so he gets himself a vampire. Springing (ex-)Queen Natasha from the "Superior Dungeon" magic penitentiary, he brings her to a realm where she can recharge on life energy and then do his bidding. But Natasha's got the need to feed, and she taps straight into the realm's lifestream, becoming ultra-powered! Gina's mystery mech foe may have bitten off more than he can chew!
